item.title: Things I Read - 6th Nov 2021
item.description: Things that I stumbled on a rainy day. Understanding how Trie (Data Structure) works Understanding how Raft (Distributed Consensus algorithm) works Trie I have heard/seen it but not in detail until now. Saw someone posted about it on HN and makes me curious. I also found post about Trie written in Python by Googling. I like the clear explaination with diagrams and put the code on github. Some takeaways Cool data structure to build autocomplete / prefix tree.
